Step 1: Creating a Telegram bot
1.1 Login to telegram account and go to BotFather
1.2 give commands
		/start - to start the BotFather bot
		/newbot - to create you own bot
1.3 give name to your bot like "juje12bot" is mine.
1.4 give unique username to your bot like "jujebot" is mine.
1.5 Now you will get a token to access HTTP API. 
		
Step 2: Install telepot package in python to code the bot in python.

Step 3: Wite python bot code and run.

Step 4: Send message to bot and bot will give response.
